Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.84,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,40)\be1\fad(50,1000)}卻還要一往無前  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.84,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,70)\be1\fad(50,1000)}それでも前に進むの Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.35,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,40)\be1\fad(0,150)}宛如夢幻般的現實
